<!doctype html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no">
<title>보험료 확인</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="../../css/directH1.css">
<script src="../../js/jquery/jquery-1.8.3.min.js"></script>
<script src="../../js/ui.js"></script>
<script src="../../js/ui_common.js"></script>
</head>

<body>
<div id="skipNavi"><a href="#h1Content">본문 바로가기</a></div>
<header>
	<h1>보험료 확인</h1>
	<a href="#none" class="btnHome">메인으로 이동</a>
	<a href="#none" class="btnInfo">3</a>
</header>
<div id="h1Wrap">
	<!-- content -->
	<div class="accodion on">
		<div>
			<a href="#" class="subConOpen" role="button">
				<strong>결제 보험료</strong>
				<span>1,000,000원<em>하위컨텐츠 열기</em></span>
			</a>
		</div>
		<div class="dataDetail">
			<ul>
				<li>
					<strong class="titl">기존 보험료</strong><span class="cost">5,000만원</span>
				</li>
				<li>
					<strong class="titl">할인</strong><span class="cost">-1,250만원</span>
					<span class="info">다이렉트 할인</span>
				</li>
			</ul>
		</div>
	</div>

	<section>
		<h2>플랜 선택</h2>
		<div class="specialsList">
			<a href="#" role="button" class="on">
				<span class="name">스마트 플랜</span>
				<span class="desc">월 938,839원</span>
			</a>
			<a href="#" role="button">
				<span class="name">스탠다드 플랜</span>
				<span class="desc">월 8,839원</span>
			</a>
			<a href="#" role="button">
				<span class="name">프리미엄 플랜</span>
				<span class="desc">월 38,839원</span>
			</a>
		</div>

		<ul class="listBox">
			<li>
				<div class="check">
					<span>
						<input type="checkbox" id="check01"><label for="check01"><span class="hide">상해사망&middot;휴유장해(골프시설 내)</span></label>
					</span>
				</div>
				<div class="item">
					<p class="tit2">상해사망&middot;휴유장해(골프시설 내)<em>5,000만원</em></p>
				</div>
				<a href="#layerPopupGolf01" class="btnLink"><span>더보기</span></a>
			</li>
			<li>
				<div class="check">
					<span>
						<input type="checkbox" id="check01"><label for="check01"><span class="hide">일괄배상 (골프시설 내)</span></label>
					</span>
				</div>
				<div class="item">
					<p class="tit2">일괄배상 (골프시설 내)<em>500만원 한도</em></p>
				</div>
				<a href="#layerPopupGolf02" class="btnLink"><span>더보기</span></a>
			</li>
			<li>
				<div class="check">
					<span>
						<input type="checkbox" id="check01"><label for="check01"><span class="hide">홀인원비용</span></label>
					</span>
				</div>
				<div class="item">
					<p class="tit2">홀인원비용<em>50만원 한도</em></p>
				</div>
				<a href="#layerPopupGolf03" class="btnLink"><span>더보기</span></a>
			</li>
			<li>
				<div class="check">
					<span>
						<input type="checkbox" id="check01"><label for="check01"><span class="hide">임시거주비용보장</span></label>
					</span>
				</div>
				<div class="item">
					<p class="tit2">임시거주비용보장<em>900만원</em></p>
				</div>
				<a href="#" class="btnLink"><span>더보기</span></a>
			</li>
		</ul>

		<div class="toggleWrap">
			<div class="tabBox open">
				<div class="toggleTitle"><a href="#none" class="toggleBtn" role="button">유의사항<span class="hide">하위콘텐츠 닫기</span></a></div>
				<div class="toggleDetail">
					<p>가입유형에 따라 가입금액의 차이가 있으므로 보장금액을 확인하시기 바랍니다.</p>
				</div>	
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="btn">
			<a href="#" role="button" class="orgSms">문자로 받기</a>
		</div>
	</section>

	<div class="accodion">
		<div>
			<a href="#" class="subConOpen" role="button">
				<strong>최종 보험료</strong>
				<span>1,000,000원<em>하위컨텐츠 열기</em></span>
			</a>
		</div>
		<div class="dataDetail">
			<ul>
				<li>
					<strong class="titl">기존 보험료</strong><span class="cost">5,000만원</span>
				</li>
				<li>
					<strong class="titl">할인</strong><span class="cost">-1,250만원</span>
					<span class="info">가족형 할인(10%), 다이렉트 할인(15%)</span>
				</li>
			</ul>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="btnWrap">
		<span><a href="#" role="button">이전</a></span>
		<span><a href="#" role="button">보험 가입하기</a></span>
	</div>
	<!-- //content -->
</div>

<div class="layerPopup" id="layerPopupGolf01">
	<div class="layerWrap">
		<h2>상해사망/후유장애 (골프시설 내)</h2>
		<div class="layerCont">
			<p>골프시설 구내에서 골프의 연습, 경기 또는 지도 (탈의, 휴식포함)중 급격하고도 우연한 외래의 사고로 생긴 상해/휴유장해손해</p>
		</div>
		<div class="layerBtn">
			<a href="#close">확인</a>
		</div>
		<a href="#close" class="layerClose">닫기</a>
	</div>
</div>
<div class="layerPopup" id="layerPopupGolf02">
	<div class="layerWrap">
		<h2>일괄배상 (골프시설 내)</h2>
		<div class="layerCont">
			<p>골프시설 구내에서 골프의 연습, 경기 또는 지도 (탈의, 휴식포함)중 제3자에게 법률적인 배상책음을 부담함으로써 입은 손해</p>
		</div>
		<div class="layerBtn">
			<a href="#close">확인</a>
		</div>
		<a href="#close" class="layerClose">닫기</a>
	</div>
</div>
<div class="layerPopup" id="layerPopupGolf03">
	<div class="layerWrap">
		<h2>홀인원비용</h2>
		<div class="layerCont">
			<p>골프경기중 홀인원을 행한 경우에 아래에 열거하는 비용</p>
			<ol class="numList">
				<li>증정용 기념품 구입 비용</li>
				<li>축하회 비용</li>
				<li>골프장에 대한 기념식수 비용</li>
				<li>동반캐디에 대한 축의금</li>
			</ol>
		</div>
		<div class="layerBtn">
			<a href="#close">확인</a>
		</div>
		<a href="#close" class="layerClose">닫기</a>
	</div>
</div>
</body>
</html>

